---
import SkillsList from "./SkillsList.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="py-24">
  <div class="space-y-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:text-xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-ubuntu font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-50 whitespace-nowrap">About Me</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 leading-relaxed col-span-2">
        <p>I didn't start my career writing components — I spent a decade inside enterprise IT, working across project management, business analysis, and data governance at one of the country's largest credit unions. That work taught me how organizations make decisions, where projects break down, and what it actually takes to create something that sticks.</p>
        <p>When I made the move to frontend development, that experience came with me. I build with React, Astro, and Tailwind CSS, with a focus on accessibility and inclusive design — but I also think about the requirements behind the interface, the stakeholders who'll champion it, and the users who'll actually live inside it. </p>
        <p>I do my best work on teams that value the whole picture as much as the finished product.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="mb-2 sm:mb-4 text-lg text-left md:text-2xl font-semibold dark:text-gray-200">Tech Stack</h3>
        <SkillsList />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>